## Summary

This documentation covers the Android-Kotlin SDK for Amplitude analytics, detailing installation via Gradle/Maven (com.amplitude:analytics-android), configuration options including batching behavior, EU data residency, and autocapture features for sessions/app lifecycles/screen views/element interactions/frustration interactions, event tracking with BaseEvent objects, user identification with Identify operations, revenue tracking with Revenue objects, plugin architecture for enrichment/destination types, and advanced features like COPPA control, advertising ID/app set ID usage, location tracking, offline mode, and multiple SDK instances.

